'''''Mandalorians: Identity and Language''''' was a reference work published by the [[Galactic Institute of Anthropology]] containing anthropological information on the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] language and culture. It was in-print circa the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], approximately one year after the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]].

